DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

90-1705. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Nichols.

On response to show cause order. Respondent Leroy Alvin Nichols is in contempt unless he pays his costs in full on or before February 1, 1993.

Moyer, C.J., would hold respondent in contempt. Holmes, J., would order respondent to show cause.
